.TH "wait_resp" 9 "wait_resp" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
wait_resp \- polls for a response or timeout to a sent AFU command
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" wait_resp
.BI "(struct afu *afu "  ","
.BI "struct afu_cmd *cmd "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "afu" 12
AFU associated with the host.
.IP "cmd" 12
AFU command that was sent.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, -errno on failure
